How Stablecoins Work (Step-by-Step)
Example: USDC
	‚Ä¢	User deposits $100
	‚Ä¢	Issuer mints 100 USDC
	‚Ä¢	USDC sent to user wallet
	‚Ä¢	User can:
	‚Ä¢	Trade
	‚Ä¢	Send
	‚Ä¢	Save
	‚Ä¢	When redeemed:
	‚Ä¢	USDC burned
	‚Ä¢	USD returned
Uses of Stablecoins (MOST IMPORTANT)
1Ô∏è.Digital Payments
	‚Ä¢	Faster than bank transfers
	‚Ä¢	Works 24/7
	‚Ä¢	Cross-border payments
2Ô∏è.Crypto Trading
	‚Ä¢	Used as base trading pair
	‚Ä¢	Avoids volatility
	‚Ä¢	Easier profit calculation
3Ô∏è. DeFi (Decentralized Finance)
Used in:
	‚Ä¢	Lending
	‚Ä¢	Borrowing
	‚Ä¢	Yield farming
	‚Ä¢	Liquidity pools
4Ô∏è.Remittances
	‚Ä¢	Send money internationally
	‚Ä¢	Low fees
	‚Ä¢	Instant settlement
5Ô∏è. Protection Against Inflation
	‚Ä¢	Used in countries with high inflation
	‚Ä¢	Acts as digital USD
6Ô∏è. CBDC Alternative
	‚Ä¢	Private digital money
	‚Ä¢	Faster innovation than government systems
